data.description: Priced to Sell! No HOA!!  Welcome to this stunning two-story residence in the highly desirable community of Harker Heights, TX. As you step through the front door, you are immediately greeted by an office space with french door, perfect for those who work from home . Continuing through the home, you'll find a spacious open-concept living room that seamlessly flows into a kitchen. A conveniently located half bathroom on the first floor adds to the practical layout of this magnificent home. Upstairs, an expansive second living space awaits, providing the perfect spot for a game room, family movie nights, or simply relaxing. The master bedroom is a luxurious retreat. Three additional generously-sized bedrooms and a full bathroom provide room for everyone to spread out. This home offers plenty of space inside and out. With quality construction, elegant design, and thoughtful details throughout, it's a place where memories are waiting to be made.
